          <comment xml:lang="en">LHV is calculated based on the elemental composition of the substance. Based on the CAS number of the substance (010034-93-2), the chemical formula of the substance is found to be: H6N2O4S, (PubChem 2020).
Reference: Kim, S., Chen, J., Cheng, T., Gindulyte, A., He, J., He, S., Li, Q., Shoemaker, B. A., Thiessen, P. A., Yu, B., Zaslavsky, L., Zhang, J., &amp; Bolton, E. E. (2019). PubChem 2019 update: improved access to chemical data. Nucleic acids research, 47(D1), D1102–D1109. https://doi.org/10.1093/nar/gky1033</comment>
        </property>
        <property propertyId="38f94dd1-d5aa-41b8-b182-c0c42985d9dc" amount="35.58" unitId="7b75baf0-cbee-45e6-bf66-af119da06553">
          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Estimated value. This price is averaged from 4 different suppliers available in the commercial webstore of alibaba. The price refers to a bulk quantity purchase. All websites were retrieved on the 19th Sept 2017. THe exchange rate used is from 2010 when 1 USD - 0.755 EUR.
Price range: 
supplier 1: 1-100 $ per kg, https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/updated-hydrazine-sulfate_60361956832.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.1.3c93b095DgIEAs&amp;s=p
supplier 2: 20-50 $ per kg, https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Hot-sale-cas-10034-93-2_758793655.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.34.3c93b095DgIEAs&amp;s=p
supplier 3: 5-100 $ per kg,   https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Delivery-stability-Hydrazine-sulfate-10034-93_60512807736.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.43.3c93b095DgIEAs
supplier 4: 1-100 $ per kg, https://www.alibaba.com/product-detail/Manufacture-Hydrazine-Sulfate-Factory-Price_60637233477.html?spm=a2700.7724838.2017115.54.3c93b095DgIEAs</comment>
        </property>
